parameters.name: DATE
parameters.description: Date in the form YYDOY where YY is the 2 digit year of 1900, and the DOY is the day-of-year (Jan 1 =1).

parameters.name: INBOUND_SECONDS
parameters.description: The second-of-day of the inbound ionopause crossing.

parameters.name: INBOUND_LATITUDE
parameters.description: The venusian latitude of the spacecraft at inbound ionopause crossing given in degrees.

parameters.name: INBOUND_LOCAL_SOLAR_TIME
parameters.description: The local solar time of the spacecraft at inbound ionopause crossing given in hours.

parameters.name: INBOUND_ALTITUDE
parameters.description: The altitude of the spacecraft at inbound ionopause crossing given in kilometers.

parameters.name: INBOUND_SOLAR_ZENITH_ANGLE
parameters.description: The solar zenith angle of the spacecraft at the inbound ionopause crossing given in degrees.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_SECONDS
parameters.description: The second-of-day of the outbound ionopause crossing.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_LATITUDE
parameters.description: The venusian latitude of the spacecraft at outbound ionopause crossing given in degrees.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_LOCAL_SOLAR_TIME
parameters.description: The local solar time of the spacecraft at outbound ionopause crossing given in hours.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_ALTITUDE
parameters.description: The altitude of the spacecraft at outbound ionopause crossing given in kilometers.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_SOLAR_ZENITH_ANGLE
parameters.description: The solar zenith angle of the spacecraft at the outbound ionopause crossing given in degrees.
